name: The Secret Garden
description:
The color of a day. A sun that ignites what it felt like as a teenager. The green grass like the salty sea rosing the sunburned legs. Color, warmth and refreshing caresses. All that is stored in the memory. 
Today I find that same green waiting for you in my secret garden, under a summer sun, wishing to refresh myself by licking ice cream from your mouth. 

TV series collection Nº10
@PandaAndrez
